SIMPLE: ejaculatory
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ejaculatory
<hw>E*jac"u*la*to*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Casting or throwing out; fitted to eject; <as>as,
<ex>ejaculatory</ex> vessels</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Suddenly darted out; uttered in short sentences;
<as>as, an <ex>ejaculatory</ex> prayer or petition</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Sudden; hasty.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Ejaculatory</xex> repentances, that take us by fits and
starts.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>L'Estrange.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Eject</ent>⟦br⟧
